Ventral head length 24 % of TL and 3.3 times internarial width. Preoral snout length 1.5 times mouth width; mouth width 30 % of ventral head length and equal to internarial space; distance between fifth gill slits 56 % of distance between first gill slits, the latter 1.9 times internarial space (
